msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "(This is the town where Haruka's picture was taken.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "(I should see if the\r\nlocals have any leads.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Hi there.\r\nIs your bar open yet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Oh, I'm still prepping things for the day.\r\nWait, you've got a baby!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "So cute! He's what, a year old?\r\nA boy, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Right, Haruto?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Oh, you only like your papa, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Actually, I'm not his father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Oh, your grandson, perhaps?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Grandson...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Right, I can see how you'd think that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Anyway, if you're about to open,\r\nwould you mind if I come in for a drink?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Not at all. I still have a few things to\r\nget ready, but, after you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Huh? Kiyo-chan, who's yer friend here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "He's a customer. You should head home\r\nsoon, Nagumo-kun. I'm about to open."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Please, have a seat. Oh, right! I should\r\nfix up a special spot for the baby."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "You, tough guy. Where y'from?\r\nY'don't look local."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "I'm from Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Tokyo, huh? I get ya, I get ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "But tell me, what's a Tokyo fella like you\r\ndoin' here? Y'don't look like no tourist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Sir, you can lay the baby in here\r\nif you want. It's the perfect size for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "So? You like it?\r\nYou're a cute little guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Thanks for this, Mama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "It's fine. This is the first time I've\r\nhad such an adorable little customer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "All I usually get around here are punks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Why ya gotta do me like that?\r\nShouldn't y'be more respectful t'yer regulars?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Nagumo-kun, put that cigarette out.\r\nIt's not good for the baby."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Besides, don't you have work to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "My work's here in yer bar. Keepin' an eye\r\non this fishy bastard is my job today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "So, Tokyo man.\r\nY'got a name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu.\r\nI won't be any trouble here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Shut it, fool. 'Round here, I decide who's\r\ntrouble and who ain't. Y'get me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "That's enough out of you! Go on, scram!\r\nYou don't get to choose who my customers are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Keep the change."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I don't like the cut of yer jib. Y'can't play\r\nthe tough guy 'gainst a yakuza like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Yer just usin' that little brat of yers\r\nto hit on my Kiyo-chan, ain'tchya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Who are you calling yours?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "What're y'lookin' at, asshole?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Getting drunk and fighting with civilians?\r\nSome yakuza you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "The hell you say!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Let's take this outside. It's hard to talk to this\r\npretty Mama with you yapping in my ear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Sir, should I call the police?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "It's all right. He'll calm down once I sober\r\nhim up a bit. Can you keep an eye on Haruto?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Alright, let's do this! I'll show ya\r\nhow we <font_kind=yakuza_italic>take care</font_kind> of guys like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "By tearin' ya to bits!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "This here's perfect.\r\nNobody to go gettin' in the way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Too late t'go cryin' fer help now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Remember, this is what ya get fer pissin' me off.\r\nDieeeeeee!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "What the hell?\r\nH-How'd I lose to you...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Had enough?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "I don't get it.\r\nWho are ya!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Don't see why you're so surprised.\r\nA child could've floored a drunk fool like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Don't you walk away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "I'm captain of the Hirose Family! Next time\r\nwe meet, I ain't lettin' ya off so easy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Jus' scurry on back to Tokyo already, y'hear!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "(Looks like I'm already making friends here.\r\nAnyway, I should get back to Haruto...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Oh, you're back.\r\nIs everything okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I see you've been\r\ntaking good care of Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Yeah, he just fell asleep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "He really is a cute kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Oh, right.\r\nHow about a drink?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "So, this is Haruto-kun's mom?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "She looks young."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "She's 19 now. She left her home in Okinawa\r\nthree years ago and apparently came here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "To this neighborhood?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Take a good look at that photo.\r\nDid you ever see her around town?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "You came here to find her, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "No, I already know where she is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "What I need now is more information.\r\nWho she met here, what she was doing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Can't you ask her that directly?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Well, not exactly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "I'm actually hoping I can find Haruto's dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "I have a hunch he's around here somewhere,\r\nbut that's about all I have to go on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. I would help you if I could,\r\nbut I don't think I recognize this girl."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "She was a famous idol before she came here.\r\nHave you ever heard of Haruka Sawamura?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "I haven't.\r\nI almost never watch TV."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Thanks for the drink.\r\nWhat do I owe you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "It's on me this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "I got to hold the cutest little baby, and you\r\nhad your evening ruined by one of my regulars."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "You mean that yakuza?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "By the way, Kiryu-san...\r\nWhere are you staying?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm not sure yet.\r\nI was about to go look."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "There won't be anywhere open\r\nat this time of day, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Oh, really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "There are some hotels outside of town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "But you're here in Onomichi to look\r\nfor Haruto-kun's dad, aren't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Staying out there might be inconvenient."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I've got it. Give me just a second,\r\nI know a guy who might have a room for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "It's nothing too luxurious, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "If you don't like it, I can help you look\r\nfor a hotel farther away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "O-Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Hello? It's Kiyomi. Good evening.\r\nSorry to call so late, Ino-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Would it be okay if one of my customers\r\nstays at the Navy Apartments for a while?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "That was Ino-kun from the local association.\r\nHe owns the room I mentioned earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "It's been empty for quite a while, so he\r\nsaid it'd be okay for you to stay there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "You've been a huge help.\r\nThank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Don't get your hopes up, though.\r\nHe hasn't kept it very clean with nobody there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "He said he'd leave a futon out, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Great."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Come back for a drink sometime if you're\r\nup for it. I'd love to see Haruto-kun again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "You've been very kind.\r\nI appreciate it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "The apartments are just down the\r\ncoastline and west from there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Got it. Next time I drop in,\r\nI'll actually buy my drinks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Looking forward to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Hey, you. Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan called me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Y'know, the mama from Snack Kiyomi.\r\nYer the fella who needs my apartment, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Oh, yeah.\r\nI'm Kiryu, and this is Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Name's Ino."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "So, what'd y'say to get\r\nKiyo-chan to like ya, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "I don't follow?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "Hmph."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Just move it along.\r\nApartment's this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Listen, if I'm not welcome, say so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Woulda said no if it weren't my\r\nKiyo-chan doin' the askin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "I got no say in it though. If the light\r\nof my life calls, I pick up the phone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "You too? A yakuza I met earlier said\r\nshe was \"his\" as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Nagumo, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I think that's the guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Three of us went t'high school together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "Nagumo and me fought\r\ntooth n' nail over Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "She got sick of our shit, though.\r\nEnded up runnin' off to Tokyo alone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "So she used to live in Tokyo..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "With her movin' back here though,\r\nit's like the fire never died."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "But man, it's kinda different with that\r\nnutsack Nagumo bein' a yakuza now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Back in the good ol' days\r\nI could knock him on his ass, y'know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "But now that he's stronger,\r\nhe acts like he owns the place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Now listen good. Don't go lettin' Kiyo-chan's\r\nkindness get to yer head, y'hear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "I'll kick ya out so fast yer head'll spin if\r\nya get any funny ideas. Remember that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Well, this here's your room."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Y'can leave whenever if yer not happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "No, I appreciate this, Ino-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "There's a futon for ya, but y'can handle the\r\nrest. It's gettin' torn down soon anyways."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "The Navy Apartments're on their last legs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Why \"navy\"?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Town's been buildin' ships fer ages."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Used to be full o' sea-farin' types."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Then some so-called \"navy\" showed up,\r\nand used these buildings as a base."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "But they weren't no real navy at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "They was probly tryin' to swindle the sailors.\r\nY'know, a buncha thugs tryin' t'look legit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Some time later, the navy got took in by\r\na yakuza group called the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "That's the yakuza that plumb fool\r\nNagumo's got his'self involved with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "He tries n' claim he's some hotshot Hirose\r\ncaptain, but it's small time. Five, six guys, tops."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "I'm not surprised."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "As for Kiyo-chan, her bar's in a former\r\nred-light district for the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "But things changed once shipbuildin' slowed\r\ndown. The good times're never comin' back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "So, you from Tokyo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "I dunno what brings ya down here,\r\nbut this ain't a place outsiders stay fer long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "I can tell. I'll be gone as soon as I'm done here.\r\nUntil then, I appreciate the room."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Hmph."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "Save yer thanks for Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "All right, it looks like this is\r\nwhere we'll be living for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "(I should buy some milk.\r\nHopefully it won't be too hard to find...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "(Things seem to close early here.\r\nBut someone's got to carry milk, right?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Man, I'm sauced as a spring turkey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Just wanna hit the sack..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Huh? Don't reckon I've seen ya 'round afore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "You know any places that might\r\nsell powdered milk around here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "I'm all out, and the kid's starving."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Hm? That little guy yer son?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Nowhere's gonna be open right now.\r\nY'oughta just put him to bed fer tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Do you know any places that might\r\nsell powdered milk around here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "Ummm, powdered milk?\r\nSorry, I don't have the slightest idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "I only just moved to the area."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "If only there were\r\nconvenience stores here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "Do you know anywhere that might\r\nsell powdered milk near here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Lemme see, coulda sworn I saw\r\nit at some place I was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "Whereabouts, though...? Only caught\r\nmy eye as I was buyin' somethin' else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Sorry, my memory's shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "But I bet they probly sell it\r\nsomewhere 'round here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "Do you know any places that might\r\nsell powdered milk around here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "Hm? C'mon with that, old guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "I'm all out, and the kid's starving.\r\nI could really use a bit of help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "An ol' grump like you's raisin' a baby?\r\nNow I seen it all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Yer woman walk out on ya\r\nor somethin'? Rough life, gramps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "I take it you don't know, then!\r\nBye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "Well, good luck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "S'gonna be fine. I'll grab a bus\r\nover t'yours this weekend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "Chi-chan, y'ain't been messin'\r\nwith other guys, have ya? Just kiddin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Can't wait to see ya again, babe.\r\nLove ya too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "Hm? Yeah, hold on a sec.\r\nWhat is it, old man? Y'need somethin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Do you know any places that might\r\nsell powdered milk around here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "Uh, Chi-chan, y'still there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "I got a mean-lookin' grandpa with\r\na kid standin' in front of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "Wanted to know if I know\r\nanyplace that's got milk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "You know one, Chi-chan!?\r\nYeah. Mhm."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "Chi-chan says try goin' to the pharmacy.\r\nS'posedly they got yer milk there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "Right, good idea.\r\nThanks for the help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Nice, Chi-chan!\r\nYer the best!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "(The pharmacy is closed too...\r\nBut this can't wait until morning!)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Excuse me!\r\nIs anyone in there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Open up, please!\r\nI need milk for a baby!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "Don't y'know how late it is?\r\nThe store's been closed fer hours!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I just need a little milk. Can you\r\nsell me some? The kid won't stop crying."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "Yer gonna have to come back tomorrow.\r\nWe're all out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "That won't work. Are there any\r\nother stores that might sell it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "'Round here...?\r\nI reckon no."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "This is bad...\r\nWhat am I supposed to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "Anyway, where're y'comin' from?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Sorry, ma'am.\r\nThere's no time for small talk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "I just need some milk. Even formula\r\nwould work. You don't know anywhere?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "Now that y'mention it, Ino might\r\nbe able to get what yer lookin' for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "Ino? The association guy?\r\nThe one who runs the Navy Apartments?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Y'know him? I bet that go-getter\r\ncan help ya out. He's a real peach."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "You know where he is by chance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Haven't the foggiest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "(Wait, Kiyomi knows his number.\r\nI should go to the bar and ask her.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "Hm? Kiryu-san!\r\nHow does Ino-kun's apartment look?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "Oh, it's not so bad. Can I ask you\r\nto contact him for me, though?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "Haruto's been bawling his eyes out for\r\na while now. I need to get some milk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "Oh, of course.\r\nJust give me a minute."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "Thank you.\r\nI'll wait outside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "Shouldn't be much longer.\r\nSorry for the wait, Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Ino-kun had some info for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "He said a barber in town had a baby recently.\r\nThey might share their milk with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "A barber?\r\nIs the shop nearby?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I wish I could show you the way,\r\nbut I need to tend the bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "It's all right. Thank you, though.\r\nI'll go take a look around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "(Is this the barber shop Kiyomi mentioned?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "Excuse me! Is anyone there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "Uh, I'm having a bit of trouble\r\nwith my baby here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "Whaddya think yer doin'!?\r\nThis is a public street!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah? And who's gonna stop me,\r\nya ol' witch? Simmer down, now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "Hey, we're talking over here.\r\nDo your business elsewhere!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "If I've gotta piss, I'm gonna piss!\r\nQuit yer yappin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Y'can't do that on someone's house!\r\nWe got rules fer a reason, y'know!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "Words aren't doing the job here.\r\nSorry, but hold this kid for a sec."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "Wh-What? Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "Look, you need to leave.\r\nYou're interrupting our conversation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "What's yer deal, gramps?\r\nY'wanna go?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "Enough. I told you to get out of here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "So yer spoilin' fer a fight, huh?\r\nYer in luck, gramps, 'cause I'll fuck ya up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "Hey, whaddya think yer doin'?\r\nY'can't make such a ruckus this time o' night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "Sorry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "I heard the owners here had a baby, so I\r\nwas just hoping for some milk for my kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "Okay, if that's all y'want.\r\nI'll go grab some fer ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "The shops 'round here all close real early."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "Y'gotta make sure ya got your milk\r\n'fore the sun goes down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I just learned that firsthand.\r\nThank you, though. You're a real lifesaver."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "Jus' get home n' feed him already.\r\nY'don't wanna let him keep bawlin' like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "Rough night, huh, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "Wait, did you come by because\r\nyou were worried about me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "Mhm. I can't ignore the helpless, I guess.\r\nSorry if I'm intruding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "I'm glad you did, honestly.\r\nWhat about your bar?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "It's all regulars over there right now.\r\nThey'll be fine without me for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "Do you have a child of your own?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "You seem good with them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "I babysat for a friend a while ago..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "Oh! I should be heading back to the bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "Have a good night.\r\nYou should try to get some rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "You'll need your energy to look for\r\nHaruto's dad tomorrow, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "Yeah, thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "See you, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "(I guess I'll just have to walk around and\r\nhope I find a lead on Haruto's dad...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "285||||4"
msgid "(Kiyomi's bar is right near here.\r\nI should stop by and thank her.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "(Oh, right. The bar wouldn't\r\nbe open at this time of day.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "Ah! Just the guy I was looking for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "I was on my way to see you, Kiryu-san.\r\nI have a favor to ask."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "Of me? What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Can you play baseball?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "Hm, I know the rules at least."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "Well, Ino-kun's on a local team, and they\r\nhave a match to play today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "One of their players is sick, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "So, he asked me to see if you'd help out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "They want me to fill in?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "No problem. This should help repay you\r\nguys for how kind you've been to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "Sorry. I don't mean to guilt trip you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "And the game's right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll walk you over to the field."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "I have to get ready first, though.\r\nCan you wait for me by the ropeway station?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "The ropeway..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "I'll meet you there soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "Okay, see you in a few."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "(This is a good way to repay Kiyomi and Ino.\r\nI need to find this ropeway...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Sorry to keep you waiting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "I just got here myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "Thank you for doing this. I know you're\r\nbusy looking for Haruto's dad right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "309||||4"
msgid "Well, there should be plenty of\r\nlocals at the game, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "It might be a good opportunity to\r\nask about Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "I'm glad that's how you feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "Okay, let's get going.\r\nI'll show you up to the field."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "Yeah, thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "314||||4"
msgid "Yo, Kiryu-san. Thanks fer comin'. One of\r\nour guys came down with somethin' today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "Y'can just think of this as\r\nyou payin' yer rent."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "Right, it's a fair trade."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "Ino-kun, there's no call for that\r\nattitude with Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "318||||4"
msgid "Gimme a break, Kiyo-chan.\r\nI know that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "Either way, he agreed to this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "Not like y'gotta come to this guy's\r\nrescue all the time, eh, Kiyo-chan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "Mind your own business, Ino-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "Cold as ice..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "323||||4"
msgid "Anyway, yer gonna be playin'\r\nright field, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "324||||4"
msgid "Shouldn't see much action out there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "We're just havin' a fun,\r\ncasual game today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "Really? Your opponents\r\nseem to have another idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "Look, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "Well ain't this an interestin' twist?\r\nWe jus' can't seem t'escape each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "330||||4"
msgid "This town really is small, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan. What're y'doin' messin'\r\naround with this guy again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "Why? 'Cause you're not okay with it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "333||||4"
msgid "'Course it ain't okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "334||||4"
msgid "Look, Kiyo-chan.\r\nY'know damn well how I feel 'bout ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "335||||4"
msgid "Bothers me t'see ya cuddlin' up t'him.\r\nCan't ya put yerself in my shoes here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "336||||4"
msgid "Hey! Quit creepin' on her, Nagumo!\r\nKiyo-chan ain't fallin' for a fool like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "337||||4"
msgid "Y'think I care what ya say, dumbass!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "339||||4"
msgid "Y'oughta watch yerself from now on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi's bar is off-limits t'ya now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "341||||4"
msgid "If I ever see ya 'round there again,\r\nI'm gon' smash yer face in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "342||||4"
msgid "He really can't help himself..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "343||||4"
msgid "Are we playing this game or what?\r\nYour bench is that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344||||4"
msgid "I know jus' fine where it is!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "345||||4"
msgid "Cap, can't you give it a rest?\r\nEveryone's waiting for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "346||||4"
msgid "Sure. This game's gon'\r\nbe one for the records!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "347||||4"
msgid "Hey, did somethin' happen\r\nwith you n' Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "348||||4"
msgid "No, he really wants to fight me, though.\r\nAnyway, do you play these guys often?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "349||||4"
msgid "Aren't they yakuza?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "350||||4"
msgid "The only yakuza're the three Hirose guys.\r\nRest of 'em are all civilians."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "352||||4"
msgid "By the by, Nagumo takes this baseball\r\nstuff real serious-like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "353||||4"
msgid "I got yer back, no matter what.\r\nY'don't gotta worry 'bout that jackass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "354||||4"
msgid "He's... amazing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "355||||4"
msgid "What the?\r\nIs this guy for real...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356||||4"
msgid "B-Bullshit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "357||||4"
msgid "The game's over, Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "358||||4"
msgid "Y'don't get... to decide...\r\nwhen this ends..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "360||||4"
msgid "Nice goin' today!\r\nI'll see ya later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "361||||4"
msgid "Sorry about that.\r\nI completely ruined your game."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "362||||4"
msgid "Nah, don't even sweat it.\r\nIt ain't yer fault, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "363||||4"
msgid "Y'know though, yer real freakin' strong!\r\nYa took on a pack of yakuza and won!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364||||4"
msgid "Hopefully that lesson got through\r\neven Nagumo's thick skull."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "365||||4"
msgid "He's right. Nagumo-kun is the one\r\nwho should apologize."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "366||||4"
msgid "I'm disappointed in his behavior problem\r\nlately. Maybe I'll stop letting him in the bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "367||||4"
msgid "Oh, good one, Kiyo-chan! Nagumo's gon'\r\nbe drier than a desert without his booze!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "369||||4"
msgid "By the way, Ino-kun.\r\nDid you find anything?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "370||||4"
msgid "Oops, almost forgot, Kiryu-san.\r\nI asked 'round about that picture fer ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "371||||4"
msgid "The guys on the team said they ain't\r\never seen this girl 'round here, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "372||||4"
msgid "I see. Thanks, I'll try asking elsewhere."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "373||||4"
msgid "Y'know, we're gon' have a team party\r\nafter this. Y'all wanna tag along?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "374||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I'll have to pass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "375||||4"
msgid "There's something else I need to be doing.\r\nI have to find this kid's father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "376||||4"
msgid "I'll have to pass too, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "377||||4"
msgid "Y'sure? Well, if y'need anythin' over at\r\nthe apartment, jus' holler, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "378||||4"
msgid "Yer part of our group now. So long as\r\ny'don't make a move on Kiyo-chan, that is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "379||||4"
msgid "Right, I'll keep that in mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380||||4"
msgid "See ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "381||||4"
msgid "I guess you still don't have\r\nany clues about Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "382||||4"
msgid "Yeah. At this rate, I'm starting to wonder\r\nif Haruka was even here to begin with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "383||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384||||4"
msgid "This isn't exactly a big town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "385||||4"
msgid "Yet I haven't found even a single person\r\nwho's laid eyes on Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "386||||4"
msgid "Maybe she just passed through. That\r\nwould explain why nobody knows her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388||||4"
msgid "And if that were the case, it's pretty\r\nunlikely I'll find Haruto's dad here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "389||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "390||||4"
msgid "I'm heading back to the apartment.\r\nI need to get changed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "391||||4"
msgid "Right. Well, do you think you\r\ncould stop by my bar afterward?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "393||||4"
msgid "I'm sure you worked up an appetite today.\r\nYou deserve a meal for all your help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "394||||4"
msgid "You don't need to do that for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "395||||4"
msgid "It's okay. I want to spend some\r\nmore time with Haruto-kun, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "396||||4"
msgid "Okay then.\r\nWell, I'll see you in a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "397||||4"
msgid "(I guess I should head to Kiyomi's bar...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "398||||4"
msgid "Welcome back. Please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "399||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "400||||4"
msgid "Hey, Mama..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "401||||4"
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "402||||4"
msgid "Why is there never anyone else here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "403||||4"
msgid "You don't mince words, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404||||4"
msgid "It's not just my bar, though. The whole\r\ndistrict has been on the decline for years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "405||||4"
msgid "These days, young people prefer the\r\ncabaret clubs in other cities to bars here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "406||||4"
msgid "Guess I should actually pay\r\nmy bill this time, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "407||||4"
msgid "Didn't I say it would be my treat?\r\nDon't embarrass me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408||||4"
msgid "My regulars still come by often.\r\nI make enough to support myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "409||||4"
msgid "Have you always run this place alone?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "410||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I suppose I have.\r\nAnyway, how about a drink?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "411||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "413||||4"
msgid "You can really throw 'em back, Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "414||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "415||||4"
msgid "Sorry fer intrudin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416||||4"
msgid "Wh-What's going on here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "417||||4"
msgid "We're from the Masuzoe Family.\r\nNagumo's been a real bad kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "418||||4"
msgid "I'm Patriarch Masuzoe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "419||||4"
msgid "We gotta have some words, Mama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "420||||4"
msgid "With me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "421||||4"
msgid "Well, it's kinda complex. Could y'ask\r\nyer friend here to step out for a bit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "423||||4"
msgid "I'm tellin' ya t'leave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424||||4"
msgid "I don't take orders from you. I'm not\r\nin the way. Just go about your business."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "425||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah? I don't mind doin' just that,\r\nbut yer not gonna like what y'see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "426||||4"
msgid "K-Kiyo-chan... Sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "427||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428||||4"
msgid "The rumors're spot-on.\r\nY'really are easy on the eyes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "429||||4"
msgid "I can see why y'wouldn't wanna go\r\ncollectin' dues from her, Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "430||||4"
msgid "But that ain't an excuse fer ya to be keepin'\r\nyer family's payments from me, y'hear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "431||||4"
msgid "M-Masuzoe-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432||||4"
msgid "Don't gimme that. I'm the patriarch of\r\nthe Yomei Alliance's Masuzoe Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "433||||4"
msgid "Why've I gotta come remindin' some two-bit\r\nfamily of imbeciles to pay their dues, huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "434||||4"
msgid "The money's late 'cause yer too soft t'collect.\r\nQuit dickin' me around!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "435||||4"
msgid "O-Our patriarch's holdin' on to the cash fer\r\nnow. Just gimme a little more time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "436||||4"
msgid "(Where did they go?\r\nThey couldn't be too far by now...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "437||||4"
msgid "Ino-san was runnin' around here\r\nlike he saw a ghost or somethin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "438||||4"
msgid "Y'think the Hirose Family's in trouble?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "439||||4"
msgid "There's some huge group o' yakuza\r\noutside the Hirose house!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440||||4"
msgid "Y'should probly steer clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "441||||4"
msgid "I saw some guy in a uniform\r\nrunning 'round here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "442||||4"
msgid "They playin' a night game or somethin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "443||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "444||||4"
msgid "Ino-san. Have you seen Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "445||||4"
msgid "Yeah, jus' now.\r\nIt ain't good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "446||||4"
msgid "Nagumo was gettin' dragged off by a group o'\r\nyakuza. I was just goin' to Hirose for help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "447||||4"
msgid "That stupid bonehead!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "448||||4"
msgid "A weak-ass punk like him never\r\nshoulda gone n' joined the yakuza!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "449||||4"
msgid "Where did you see them?\r\nAnd where were they going?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "450||||4"
msgid "Looked like the top o' the hill."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "451||||4"
msgid "Y'don't gotta go yerself, Kiryu-san.\r\nJus' let the Hirose Family handle Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452||||4"
msgid "I can't afford to wait that long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "453||||4"
msgid "I've seen how strong y'are,\r\nbut y'can't take on the yakuza by yerself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "454||||4"
msgid "Those guys're way tougher than Nagumo.\r\nThere were a bunch of 'em, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "455||||4"
msgid "I know that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "456||||4"
msgid "So, where's this hill you mentioned?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "457||||4"
msgid "Up at the top o' the ropeway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "458||||4"
msgid "The tram's not runnin' at night, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "459||||4"
msgid "If y'wanna head up there now,\r\nyer gonna hafta take the footpath!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "460||||4"
msgid "Thanks for the info.\r\nI'm going to head up there now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "462||||4"
msgid "Look, y'don't gotta do this. Jus' wait for\r\nhis family. Nobody's expectin' yer help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464||||4"
msgid "Y'know how they're holdin' ya right now?\r\nIt's called the jet style."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "465||||4"
msgid "In ancient China, this is how they used\r\nt'punish traitors. Suits ya, don't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "466||||4"
msgid "Patriarch Masuzoe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "467||||4"
msgid "Nagumo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "468||||4"
msgid "What're y'doin' here?\r\nAin't you the guy from the bar?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "469||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "470||||4"
msgid "You were really stupid enough t'follow\r\nus all the way up here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "471||||4"
msgid "Why d'ya care about Nagumo so much, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "472||||4"
msgid "Because I'm his fighting rival now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "473||||4"
msgid "Your fighting rival?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "474||||4"
msgid "G-Get outta here, Kiryu! Y'can't go stickin'\r\nyer nose into yakuza business, dumbass!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "475||||4"
msgid "Yakuza or not, I don't really care.\r\nThese guys made my baby cry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "476||||4"
msgid "And I'm not walking away until I get\r\nan apology for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "477||||4"
msgid "Y'been drinkin', old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "478||||4"
msgid "If y'wanna pick a fight with us,\r\nwe'd be real glad to oblige."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "479||||4"
msgid "Can't guarantee you'll live, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "480||||4"
msgid "I don't want to fight you, but I'll do\r\nwhat I have to if you won't apologize."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "481||||4"
msgid "Wh-What're y'doin', Kiryu!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "482||||4"
msgid "The Masuzoe Family ain't gonna forgive\r\nya for this. Yer diggin' yer own grave!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "483||||4"
msgid "You're worried about me now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "484||||4"
msgid "Y-Ya dumbass!\r\nWhy would I be worried!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "485||||4"
msgid "It's just, if ya get yerself killed by these\r\nguys, Kiyo-chan's gonna be real sad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "486||||4"
msgid "You're not such a bad guy after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "487||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "488||||4"
msgid "You two lovebirds done yappin'!?\r\nHow long d'we gotta listen to this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "490||||4"
msgid "Yer an interestin' fella, though.\r\nI'll spare yer life this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "491||||4"
msgid "Let's give 'im his fight. I'm sure he'll\r\nsober up once he gets a piece o' us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "492||||4"
msgid "Uh, I gotta warn ya, though... This guy\r\nain't just yer run o'the mill civilian..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "493||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "494||||4"
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "495||||4"
msgid "Y'really beat 'em..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "496||||4"
msgid "I don't get it. Those're Masuzoe yakuza.\r\nAnd there were five of 'em..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "497||||4"
msgid "Man... Yer really somethin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "498||||4"
msgid "Can you stand, Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "499||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Why'd y'come n'\r\nsave an asshole like me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "500||||4"
msgid "A man always wants to impress\r\nthe woman he loves, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "501||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "502||||4"
msgid "Anyone would agree with that. They can't\r\nlook weak in front of her, no matter what."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "503||||4"
msgid "They need to stay strong for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "504||||4"
msgid "But, when push comes to shove,\r\nnot many would risk their lives over it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "505||||4"
msgid "Back in the bar, you stood your ground when\r\nmost would have crumbled. That took guts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "507||||4"
msgid "I couldn't let a guy like that wind up dead.\r\nSo I figured I'd come up here and save you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "509||||4"
msgid "Guess I lose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "510||||4"
msgid "I ain't ever gonna beat a guy like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "511||||4"
msgid "I don't even mind losin' Kiyo-chan if y'were\r\nthe one to take her. I'd step aside fer ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512||||4"
msgid "Don't worry.\r\nI didn't come for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "513||||4"
msgid "Either way, so long as yer hangin' around,\r\nKiyo-chan'd never go fer an idiot like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "514||||4"
msgid "Forget that fer now, though.\r\nI jus' decided somethin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "515||||4"
msgid "What now?"
msgstr ""

